Controls which GUI actions are logged. The choices are: 
 all: all GUI actions; 
 db: GUI actions that affect the DB like gui_select, set_layer_preference, but not display-only actions like gui_zoom, gui_pan; 
 none: no gui_* commands are logged, so the .log and .cmd file are incomplete Type: enum Enum Values: all db none 
